      "writtenOn": "2021-02-23T14:47:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Do you have a link?  This regex doesn\u0027t match up with the definitions from the Git manual, in particular that the key and value are separated by a colon and a space.",
      "parentUuid": "4ca07f54_d8c6be6c",
      "revId": "04a767522195053054de61818628c6b29a5c238a",
